		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">(what is the point to get one screen mirroring if you cannot switch between screens ?).</div>
<br />In a mapper where the only choices are map A, horizontal mirroring, and vertical mirroring, one can use map A for the scrolling screen and map B (which does not scroll) for a status bar.

		

